<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Réinitialisation de mot de passe — IWasThere</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0B0D10;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:32px auto;background:#111318;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)">

        {# Header #}
        <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e 0%,#0d1220 100%);padding:32px 24px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)">
            <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:52px;height:52px;background:rgba(61,220,151,0.12);border-radius:14px;border:1px solid rgba(61,220,151,0.25);margin-bottom:12px">
                <span style="font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#3DDC97">IW</span>
            </div>
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#F2F3F5;letter-spacing:-0.01em">IWasThere</h1>
        </div>

        {# Body #}
        <div style="padding:32px 24px">
            <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#F2F3F5">Réinitialisation de mot de passe</h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:14px;color:#9CA3AF;line-height:1.6">
                Bonjour {{ user.displayName }},<br><br>
                Tu as demandé à réinitialiser ton mot de passe. Clique sur le bouton ci-dessous pour en choisir un nouveau.
                Ce lien est valable <strong style="color:#F2F3F5">1 heure</strong>.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0">
                <a href="{{ reset_url }}"
                   style="display:inline-block;background:#3DDC97;color:#0B0D10;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em">
                    Réinitialiser mon mot de passe
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.6">
                Si tu n'as pas demandé cette réinitialisation, ignore cet email — ton mot de passe restera inchangé.
            </p>

            <div style="margin-top:8px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)">
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#4B5563">
                    Ou copie ce lien dans ton navigateur :<br>
                    <span style="color:#60A5FA;word-break:break-all">{{ reset_url }}</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# Footer #}
        <div style="padding:16px 24px;background:#0d0f14;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);text-align:center">
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#4B5563">
                IWasThere — Ton journal d'expériences live
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
